If you decide to register with Facebook Connect and click on the ‚ÄúLogin with Facebook‚Äù/‚ÄùConnect with Facebook‚Äù button, you will automatically be redirected to the Facebook platform. There you can log in with your user data. This will link your Facebook profile to our services. Through this link, we gain access to your data stored on Facebook. These are mainly:
