The provider is Amazon Web Services EMEA SARL, 38 Avenue John F Kennedy, 1855 Luxembourg (hereinafter: AWS). When you visit our website, your personal data is processed on the AWS servers. Personal data may also be transferred to the parent company of AWS in the USA. Data transmission to the USA is based on the EU standard contractual clauses. Details can be found here:
https://aws.amazon.com/de/blogs/security/aws-gdpr-data-processing-addendum/
