https://www.jamsadr.com/DPF-Dispute-Resolution
for more information or to file a complaint.¬† The services of JAMS are provided at no cost to you.¬† Following the dispute resolution process, JAMS or you may refer the matter to the U.S. Federal Trade Commission, which has investigatory and enforcement powers over us. Under certain circumstances, you also may be able to invoke binding arbitration to address complaints about our compliance with DPF Principles.
